OL,3,CClimate change 'worsened all 10
OL,4,Cdeadliest weather events in past two
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FClimate change contributed to all ten
OL,8,Fof the world's deadliest extreme
OL,9,Fweather events in the past two
OL,10,Fdecades, scientists have concluded.
OL,12,FAmong them was the 2022 heatwave which
OL,13,Fgripped much of Europe, bringing
OL,14,Frecord 40C temperatures to parts of
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,FThe assessment comes from the World
OL,18,FWeather Attribution group, which
OL,19,Fanalyses the impact of climate change
OL,20,Fon extreme weather events in their
OL,21,Fimmediate aftermath.
