OL,3,CClimate change 'worsened all 10
OL,4,Cdeadliest weather events in past two
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FIt says the ten deadliest global
OL,8,Fevents, which include three tropical
OL,9,Fcyclones, four heatwaves, a drought
OL,10,Fand two floods, between them resulted
OL,11,Fin the deaths of least 576,042 people.
OL,13,FIt says "the fingerprints of climate
OL,14,Fchange" are evident in all these
OL,15,Fevents, making them more intense as
OL,16,Fwell as more likely to have happened
OL,17,Fin the first place.
