OL,3,CClimate change 'worsened all 10
OL,4,Cdeadliest weather events in past two
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FThey warned the death toll is a "major
OL,8,Funderestimate", as there may have been
OL,9,Fmillions more heat-related deaths not
OL,10,Freported in official statistics.
OL,12,FScientists said the findings
OL,13,Funderscore "how dangerous extreme
OL,14,Fweather events have already become"
OL,15,Fwith just 1.3C of global warming above
OL,16,Fpre-industrial levels.
OL,18,FThey highlight the urgency of cutting
OL,19,Fgreenhouse gas emissions which are
OL,20,Fdriving rising temperatures and more
OL,21,Fextreme weather.
