OL,3,CClimate change 'worsened all 10
OL,4,Cdeadliest weather events in past two
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FDr Friederike Otto, co-founder and
OL,8,Flead of World Weather Attribution at
OL,9,Fthe Centre for Environmental Policy,
OL,10,FImperial College London, said:
OL,11,F"Climate change isn't a distant threat.
OL,13,F"This study should be an eye-opener
OL,14,Ffor political leaders hanging on to
OL,15,Ffossil fuels that heat the planet and
OL,16,Fdestroy lives.
OL,18,F"If we keep burning oil, gas and coal,
OL,19,Fthe suffering will continue."
