OL,3,CClimate change 'worsened all 10
OL,4,Cdeadliest weather events in past two
OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FThe researchers said many of the
OL,8,Fdeaths caused by extreme weather were
OL,9,Favoidable.
OL,11,FThey said countries should ramp up
OL,12,Fefforts to be prepared, including
OL,13,Fimplementing early warning systems and
OL,14,Fboosting resilience in cities with
OL,15,Fmeasures such as wetlands, green
OL,16,Froofs, urban forests and emergency
OL,17,Fshelters, and make sure infrastructure
OL,18,Fsuch as dams are climate-proofed so
OL,19,Fthey will not fail.
