OL,5,Cdecades'
OL,7,FBut there are limits to how much
OL,8,Fcommunities can adapt to some of the
OL,9,Fmost extreme events the world is
OL,10,Fseeing and these will become more
OL,11,Ffrequent as long as fossil fuel use
OL,12,Fcontinues to push up global
OL,13,Ftemperatures, they said.
